31
00:01:58,760 --> 00:01:59,599
The two of us...

32
00:01:59,599 --> 00:02:00,840
...still have some things to go over.

33
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:01,799
So...

34
00:02:01,799 --> 00:02:02,840
Mom, how about...

35
