74
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,759
Listen to me.

75
00:03:11,039 --> 00:03:12,879
This time, you better perk up.

76
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:13,879
Do you hear me?

77
00:03:14,759 --> 00:03:15,840
Before you turn thirty...

78
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:17,960
