92
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,840
We're together.

93
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:47,960
Together doing what, exactly?

94
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,280
It means the two of us...

95
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:50,840
...are together.

96
00:03:53,039 --> 00:03:53,800
Yes.

97
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,800
