229
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,200
Let me show you.

230
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,000
Let's see, let's see.

231
00:11:37,039 --> 00:11:38,000
Nice figure.

232
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:39,480
