233
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:40,279
Hey, let me see.

234
00:11:40,759 --> 00:11:43,120
Maybe the front isn't much to look at.

235
00:11:44,279 --> 00:11:46,440
Our President Qin has been single since birth.

236
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:47,960
