239
00:11:52,519 --> 00:11:53,120
Right.

240
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:54,080
Too naive.

241
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:54,639
Yeah.

242
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:56,480
